description.en: Tachyon Protocol is a decentralized internet protocol co-launched by V SYSTEMS and X-VPN that aims to create a stable, fast and reliable new internet by improving TCP/IP model. IPX is the native cryptocurrency of the Tachyon network that resides on the V SYSTEMS blockchain which serves a clear purpose and utility in the overall Tachyon ecosystem.
